com.solution2013.field

Class SpaceWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.solution2013.field.SpaceWrapper

  • public class SpaceWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps a Space in a node for use in DIjkstra's algorithm. This allows us to run multiple distance calculations on the same Spaces without worrying about corruption between them because each calculation uses new SpaceWrappers
    Author:
    Daniel Centore
